{"tid":1256990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《逃犯條例》教材,街站宣傳素材","createTime":"2019-06-25T10:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T03:00:10.000Z","uid":201879,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7471bacf00c5a701aba9130f8e2073fef0619c8","tid":1256990,"uid":201879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"有中學通識科老師製作左給予學生認識《逃犯條例》的教材, 放上黎畀各位用,除左畀學生之外,亦適合作為街站宣傳素材。<br />\n<br />\n內容:<br />\n1. 由1997年回歸為起點的事件發展時間線 (目前時間線更新到18/6 林鄭於記者招待會向市民道歉)<br />\n2. 以事件為主軸，修改《逃犯條例》帶來的社會爭議<br />\n3. 不同持份者對修改《逃犯條例》的看法<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位取用及修改。如有錯漏，請自行修改。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wBxgFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wBxgFS.jpg&h=81812b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmWhsNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmWhsNx.jpg&h=3ab20cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFv6k7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFv6k7y.jpg&h=309e2232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0V9F90U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0V9F90U.jpg&h=476b537b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D206k7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD206k7A.jpg&h=3818b3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ui2wxeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUi2wxeg.jpg&h=793f8650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmaiceh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftmaiceh.jpg&h=58e67aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6feu0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6feu0Y.jpg&h=3b9cfd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/